***********************************************************
*            GPGPU2 ASSIGNMENT - ASTROMINER               *
***********************************************************
AstroMiner implementation to run on both CPU and GPU.

-- How to compile?
CMake is used to create the necessary makefiles. Please install CMake and execute the following in the main directory:
> CMake CMakeLists.txt
> make

-- How to run?
In order to run, simply execute AstroMiner with the necessary options (run with no options to see available options) 
